Still to come on the "NewsHour":
the vice chair of the Senate
Intelligence Committee

09:08.233 --> 09:13.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
on revelations that
President Trump is under
scrutiny for potentially
obstructing the Russia

09:15.233 --> 09:19.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
investigation; arrest warrants
issued after a violent clash
outside the Turkish Embassy;

09:21.133 --> 09:25.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a government visa
program receives renewed
criticism; and much more.

